The paper discusses the security and performance of a dynamic proof of retrievability (POR) scheme for cloud storage, which involves cryptography and data management. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security), followed by cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing), cs.DB (Databases), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), and cs.SE (Software Engineering).
